                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>Marble plaque in seven fragments, with sections missing at the top edge. Text is contained within a simple carved entabulature. This inscription reuses an earlier inscription, a dedication to Domitian (CIL 9.4952).</p>
                                    <material ana="#material.stone.marble" ref="https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html">Marble</material> 
