                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote><p>The first four lines of the text are significantly different from the last two. The text in the first two lines is broad and clear, although the stone carver appears to have run out of room in line 4, and the final "G" is small.The final two lines are much thinner and uneven, and the text is crowded. Presence of irregular interpuncts throughout.</p>
                                <locus from="line1" to="line6">Lines 1–6</locus>
